          "explanation": "(d) Spheno-ethmoidal recess(Ref. Cummings, 6th ed., 659)The Sphenoid sinus opens into the spheno-ethmoidal recess just above the superior turbinate.",
          "hint": "Topic: Congenital Lesions and Stridor"
