          "explanation": "Ans. is 'c' i.e.. Nasal Smear o A nasal smear can sometimes be helpful for establishing the diagnosis of allergic rhinitis.o The presence of eosinophils is consistent with allergic rhinitis.",
          "hint": "Topic: Nose and PNS"
