          "correctOptionId": "opt-2",
          "explanation": "EXTERNAL CAROTID SYSTEM 1. Sphenopalatine aery (branch of maxillary aery) gives nasopalatine and posterior medial nasal branches. 2. Septal branch of greater palatine aery (branch of max- illary aery). 3. Septal branch of superior labial aery (branch of facial aery). Ref : ENT textbook by Dhingra 6th edition Pgno : 177",
          "hint": "Topic: All India exam"
