          "explanation": "Situated above the lateral process of malleus between the notch of Rivinus and the anterior and posterior malleal folds.Reissner's membrane - Separates scala media from scala vestibuli in the inner earBasilar membrane - Seen in scala media and suppos the organ of coiSecondary Tympanic Membrane - Closes the scala tympani at the site of round window"
