          "correctOptionId": "opt-1",
          "explanation": "Development of pars superior (semicircular canals and utricle) takes place earlier than pars inferior (saccule and cochlea). The pars superior is phylogenetically older pa of labyrinth.",
          "hint": "Topic: NEET Jan 2020"
