          "id": "medmcqa-e2ca00b2-bc25-411b-81bc-9c954c87ffd4",
          "text": "An 70 yrs. aged patient with epistaxis , patient is hypertensive with B.P = 200/110 mm Hg. On examination no active bleeding noted, next step of management is:",
